{"word":"G2837 - κοιμάω - koimáō - koy-mah'-o - Sleep","slug":"G2837","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοιμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>koimáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>koy-mah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Sleep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - koimao&#x0304;</b> - <i>koy-mah'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>; to <i>put to sleep</i>, that is, (passively or reflexively) to <i>slumber</i>; figuratively to <i>decease:</i> - (be a-, fall a-, fall on) sleep, be dead."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2838\">G2838</a>"}]}